-- Equality properties
 
lift-resp : ‚àÄ {_‚âà_ : Rel A ‚Ñì} ‚Üí P Respects _‚âà_ ‚Üí
            (Any P) Respects (Pointwise _‚âà_)
lift-resp resp (x‚âày ‚à∑ xs‚âàys) (here px)   = here (resp x‚âày px)
lift-resp resp (x‚âày ‚à∑ xs‚âàys) (there pxs) = there (lift-resp resp xs‚âàys pxs)
 
here-injective : ‚àÄ {p q : P x} ‚Üí here {P = P} {xs = xs} p ‚â° here q ‚Üí p ‚â° q
here-injective refl = refl
 
there-injective : ‚àÄ {p q : Any P xs} ‚Üí there {x = x} p ‚â° there q ‚Üí p ‚â° q
there-injective refl = refl

-- Any is a congruence
 
Any-cong : ‚àÄ {k : Kind} ‚Üí (‚àÄ x ‚Üí Related k (P x) (Q x)) ‚Üí
           (‚àÄ {z} ‚Üí Related k (z ‚àà xs) (z ‚àà ys)) ‚Üí
           Related k (Any P xs) (Any Q ys)

  Any P xs                ‚Üî‚ü® Related.SK-sym Any‚Üî ‚ü©
  (‚àÉ Œª x ‚Üí x ‚àà xs √ó P x)  ‚àº‚ü® Œ£.cong Inverse.‚Üî-refl (xs‚âàys √ó-cong P‚ÜîQ _) ‚ü©
  (‚àÉ Œª x ‚Üí x ‚àà ys √ó Q x)  ‚Üî‚ü® Any‚Üî ‚ü©
  Any Q ys                ‚àé
  where open Related.EquationalReasoning

-- Any.map
 
map-cong : (f g : P ‚ãê Q) ‚Üí (‚àÄ {x} (p : P x) ‚Üí f p ‚â° g p) ‚Üí
          (p : Any P xs) ‚Üí Any.map f p ‚â° Any.map g p
map-cong f g hyp (here  p) = cong here (hyp p)
map-cong f g hyp (there p) = cong there $ map-cong f g hyp p
 
map-id : ‚àÄ (f : P ‚ãê P) ‚Üí (‚àÄ {x} (p : P x) ‚Üí f p ‚â° p) ‚Üí
         (p : Any P xs) ‚Üí Any.map f p ‚â° p
map-id f hyp (here  p) = cong here (hyp p)
map-id f hyp (there p) = cong there $ map-id f hyp p
 
map-‚àò : ‚àÄ (f : Q ‚ãê R) (g : P ‚ãê Q) (p : Any P xs) ‚Üí
        Any.map (f ‚àò g) p ‚â° Any.map f (Any.map g p)
map-‚àò f g (here  p) = refl
map-‚àò f g (there p) = cong there $ map-‚àò f g p
 
------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- Any.lookup
 
lookup-result : ‚àÄ (p : Any P xs) ‚Üí P (Any.lookup p)
lookup-result (here px) = px
lookup-result (there p) = lookup-result p
 
lookup-index : ‚àÄ (p : Any P xs) ‚Üí P (lookup xs (Any.index p))
lookup-index (here px)   = px
lookup-index (there pxs) = lookup-index pxs

-- Swapping
 
-- Nested occurrences of Any can sometimes be swapped. See also √ó‚Üî.
 
module _ {R : REL A B ‚Ñì} where
 
  swap : Any (Œª x ‚Üí Any (R x) ys) xs ‚Üí Any (Œª y ‚Üí Any (flip R y) xs) ys
  swap (here  pys)  = Any.map here pys
  swap (there pxys) = Any.map there (swap pxys)
 
  swap-there : (any : Any (Œª x ‚Üí Any (R x) ys) xs) ‚Üí
               swap (Any.map (there {x = x}) any) ‚â° there (swap any)
  swap-there (here  pys)  = refl
  swap-there (there pxys) = cong (Any.map there) (swap-there pxys)
 
module _ {R : REL A B ‚Ñì} where
 
  swap-invol : (any : Any (Œª x ‚Üí Any (R x) ys) xs) ‚Üí
               swap (swap any) ‚â° any
  swap-invol (here (here px))   = refl
  swap-invol (here (there pys)) =
    cong (Any.map there) (swap-invol (here pys))
  swap-invol (there pxys)       =
    trans (swap-there (swap pxys)) (cong there (swap-invol pxys))
 
module _ {R : REL A B ‚Ñì} where
 
  swap‚Üî : Any (Œª x ‚Üí Any (R x) ys) xs ‚Üî Any (Œª y ‚Üí Any (flip R y) xs) ys
  swap‚Üî = mk‚Üî‚Çõ‚Ä≤ swap swap swap-invol swap-invol

-- Lemmas relating Any to ‚ä§
 
-- These introduction and elimination rules are not inverses, though.
 
any‚Å∫ : ‚àÄ (p : A ‚Üí Bool) ‚Üí Any (T ‚àò p) xs ‚Üí T (any p xs)
any‚Å∫ p (here  px)          = Equivalence.from T-‚à® (inj‚ÇÅ px)
any‚Å∫ p (there {x = x} pxs) with p x
... | true  = _
... | false = any‚Å∫ p pxs
 
any‚Åª : ‚àÄ (p : A ‚Üí Bool) xs ‚Üí T (any p xs) ‚Üí Any (T ‚àò p) xs
any‚Åª p (x ‚à∑ xs) px‚à∑xs with p x in eq
... | true  = here (Equivalence.from T-‚â° eq)
... | false = there (any‚Åª p xs px‚à∑xs)
 
any‚áî : ‚àÄ {p : A ‚Üí Bool} ‚Üí Any (T ‚àò p) xs ‚áî T (any p xs)
any‚áî = mk‚áî (any‚Å∫ _) (any‚Åª _ _)

-- Sums commute with Any
 
Any-‚äé‚Å∫ : Any P xs ‚äé Any Q xs ‚Üí Any (Œª x ‚Üí P x ‚äé Q x) xs
Any-‚äé‚Å∫ = [ Any.map inj‚ÇÅ , Any.map inj‚ÇÇ ]‚Ä≤
 
Any-‚äé‚Åª : Any (Œª x ‚Üí P x ‚äé Q x) xs ‚Üí Any P xs ‚äé Any Q xs
Any-‚äé‚Åª (here (inj‚ÇÅ p)) = inj‚ÇÅ (here p)
Any-‚äé‚Åª (here (inj‚ÇÇ q)) = inj‚ÇÇ (here q)
Any-‚äé‚Åª (there p)       = Sum.map there there (Any-‚äé‚Åª p)
 
‚äé‚Üî : (Any P xs ‚äé Any Q xs) ‚Üî Any (Œª x ‚Üí P x ‚äé Q x) xs
‚äé‚Üî {P = P} {Q = Q} = mk‚Üî‚Çõ‚Ä≤ Any-‚äé‚Å∫ Any-‚äé‚Åª to‚àòfrom from‚àòto
  where
  from‚àòto : (p : Any P xs ‚äé Any Q xs) ‚Üí Any-‚äé‚Åª (Any-‚äé‚Å∫ p) ‚â° p
  from‚àòto (inj‚ÇÅ (here  p)) = refl
  from‚àòto (inj‚ÇÅ (there p)) rewrite from‚àòto (inj‚ÇÅ p) = refl
  from‚àòto (inj‚ÇÇ (here  q)) = refl
  from‚àòto (inj‚ÇÇ (there q)) rewrite from‚àòto (inj‚ÇÇ q) = refl
 
  to‚àòfrom : (p : Any (Œª x ‚Üí P x ‚äé Q x) xs) ‚Üí Any-‚äé‚Å∫ (Any-‚äé‚Åª p) ‚â° p
  to‚àòfrom (here (inj‚ÇÅ p)) = refl
  to‚àòfrom (here (inj‚ÇÇ q)) = refl
  to‚àòfrom (there p) with Any-‚äé‚Åª p | to‚àòfrom p
  ... | inj‚ÇÅ p | refl = refl
  ... | inj‚ÇÇ q | refl = refl

-- Products "commute" with Any.
 
Any-√ó‚Å∫ : Any P xs √ó Any Q ys ‚Üí Any (Œª x ‚Üí Any (Œª y ‚Üí P x √ó Q y) ys) xs
Any-√ó‚Å∫ (p , q) = Any.map (Œª p ‚Üí Any.map (Œª q ‚Üí (p , q)) q) p
 
Any-√ó‚Åª : Any (Œª x ‚Üí Any (Œª y ‚Üí P x √ó Q y) ys) xs ‚Üí
         Any P xs √ó Any Q ys

            let y , y‚ààys , p , q = find pq‚Ä≤ in
            lose x‚ààxs p , lose y‚ààys q

  to‚àòfrom : ‚àÄ pq ‚Üí Any-√ó‚Å∫ (Any-√ó‚Åª pq) ‚â° pq

-- Half-applied product commutes with Any.
 
module _ {_~_ : REL A B r} where
 
  Any-Œ£‚Å∫ ≥ : (‚àÉ Œª x ‚Üí Any (_~ x) xs) ‚Üí Any (‚àÉ ‚àò _~_) xs
  Any-Œ£‚Å∫ ≥ (b , here px) = here (b , px)
  Any-Œ£‚Å∫ ≥ (b , there pxs) = there (Any-Œ£‚Å∫ ≥ (b , pxs))
 
  Any-Œ£‚Åª ≥ : Any (‚àÉ ‚àò _~_) xs ‚Üí ‚àÉ Œª x ‚Üí Any (_~ x) xs
  Any-Œ£‚Åª ≥ (here (b , x)) = b , here x
  Any-Œ£‚Åª ≥ (there xs) = Product.map‚ÇÇ there $ Any-Œ£‚Åª ≥ xs

-- map
 
module _ {f : A ‚Üí B} where
 
  map‚Å∫ : Any (P ‚àò f) xs ‚Üí Any P (List.map f xs)
  map‚Å∫ (here p)  = here p
  map‚Å∫ (there p) = there $ map‚Å∫ p
 
  map‚Åª : Any P (List.map f xs) ‚Üí Any (P ‚àò f) xs
  map‚Åª {xs = x ‚à∑ xs} (here p)  = here p
  map‚Åª {xs = x ‚à∑ xs} (there p) = there $ map‚Åª p
 
  map‚Å∫‚àòmap‚Åª : (p : Any P (List.map f xs)) ‚Üí map‚Å∫ (map‚Åª p) ‚â° p
  map‚Å∫‚àòmap‚Åª {xs = x ‚à∑ xs} (here  p) = refl
  map‚Å∫‚àòmap‚Åª {xs = x ‚à∑ xs} (there p) = cong there (map‚Å∫‚àòmap‚Åª p)
 
  map‚Åª‚àòmap‚Å∫ : ‚àÄ (P : Pred B p) ‚Üí
              (p : Any (P ‚àò f) xs) ‚Üí map‚Åª {P = P} (map‚Å∫ p) ‚â° p
  map‚Åª‚àòmap‚Å∫ P (here  p) = refl
  map‚Åª‚àòmap‚Å∫ P (there p) = cong there (map‚Åª‚àòmap‚Å∫ P p)
 
  map‚Üî : Any (P ‚àò f) xs ‚Üî Any P (List.map f xs)
  map‚Üî = mk‚Üî‚Çõ‚Ä≤ map‚Å∫ map‚Åª map‚Å∫‚àòmap‚Åª (map‚Åª‚àòmap‚Å∫ _)
 
  gmap : P ‚ãê Q ‚àò f ‚Üí Any P ‚ãê Any Q ‚àò map f
  gmap g = map‚Å∫ ‚àò Any.map g

-- mapMaybe
 
module _ (f : A ‚Üí Maybe B) where
 
  mapMaybe‚Å∫ : ‚àÄ xs ‚Üí Any (MAny.Any P) (map f xs) ‚Üí Any P (mapMaybe f xs)
  mapMaybe‚Å∫ (x ‚à∑ xs) ps with f x | ps
  ... | nothing | there pxs      = mapMaybe‚Å∫ xs pxs
  ... | just _  | here (just py) = here py
  ... | just _  | there pxs      = there (mapMaybe‚Å∫ xs pxs)

-- _++_
 
module _ {P : A ‚Üí Set p} where
 
  ++‚Å∫À° : Any P xs ‚Üí Any P (xs ++ ys)
  ++‚Å∫À° (here p)  = here p
  ++‚Å∫À° (there p) = there (++‚Å∫À° p)
 
  ++‚Å∫ ≥ : ‚àÄ xs {ys} ‚Üí Any P ys ‚Üí Any P (xs ++ ys)
  ++‚Å∫ ≥ []       p = p
  ++‚Å∫ ≥ (x ‚à∑ xs) p = there (++‚Å∫ ≥ xs p)
 
  ++‚Åª : ‚àÄ xs {ys} ‚Üí Any P (xs ++ ys) ‚Üí Any P xs ‚äé Any P ys
  ++‚Åª []       p         = inj‚ÇÇ p
  ++‚Åª (x ‚à∑ xs) (here p)  = inj‚ÇÅ (here p)
  ++‚Åª (x ‚à∑ xs) (there p) = Sum.map there id (++‚Åª xs p)
 
  ++‚Å∫‚àò++‚Åª : ‚àÄ xs {ys} (p : Any P (xs ++ ys)) ‚Üí [ ++‚Å∫À° , ++‚Å∫ ≥ xs ]‚Ä≤ (++‚Åª xs p) ‚â° p
  ++‚Å∫‚àò++‚Åª []       p         = refl
  ++‚Å∫‚àò++‚Åª (x ‚à∑ xs) (here  p) = refl
  ++‚Å∫‚àò++‚Åª (x ‚à∑ xs) (there p) with ih ‚Üê ++‚Å∫‚àò++‚Åª xs p | ++‚Åª xs p
  ... | inj‚ÇÅ _ = cong there ih
  ... | inj‚ÇÇ _ = cong there ih
 
  ++‚Åª‚àò++‚Å∫ : ‚àÄ xs {ys} (p : Any P xs ‚äé Any P ys) ‚Üí
            ++‚Åª xs ([ ++‚Å∫À° , ++‚Å∫ ≥ xs ]‚Ä≤ p) ‚â° p
  ++‚Åª‚àò++‚Å∫ []            (inj‚ÇÇ p)         = refl
  ++‚Åª‚àò++‚Å∫ (x ‚à∑ xs)      (inj‚ÇÅ (here  p)) = refl
  ++‚Åª‚àò++‚Å∫ (x ‚à∑ xs) {ys} (inj‚ÇÅ (there p)) rewrite ++‚Åª‚àò++‚Å∫ xs {ys} (inj‚ÇÅ p) = refl
  ++‚Åª‚àò++‚Å∫ (x ‚à∑ xs)      (inj‚ÇÇ p)         rewrite ++‚Åª‚àò++‚Å∫ xs      (inj‚ÇÇ p) = refl
 
  ++‚Üî : ‚àÄ {xs ys} ‚Üí (Any P xs ‚äé Any P ys) ‚Üî Any P (xs ++ ys)
  ++‚Üî {xs = xs} = mk‚Üî‚Çõ‚Ä≤ [ ++‚Å∫À° , ++‚Å∫ ≥ xs ]‚Ä≤ (++‚Åª xs) (++‚Å∫‚àò++‚Åª xs) (++‚Åª‚àò++‚Å∫ xs)
 
  ++-comm : ‚àÄ xs ys ‚Üí Any P (xs ++ ys) ‚Üí Any P (ys ++ xs)
  ++-comm xs ys = [ ++‚Å∫ ≥ ys , ++‚Å∫À° ]‚Ä≤ ‚àò ++‚Åª xs
 
  ++-comm‚àò++-comm : ‚àÄ xs {ys} (p : Any P (xs ++ ys)) ‚Üí
                    ++-comm ys xs (++-comm xs ys p) ‚â° p
  ++-comm‚àò++-comm [] {ys} p
    rewrite ++‚Åª‚àò++‚Å∫ ys {ys = []} (inj‚ÇÅ p) = refl
  ++-comm‚àò++-comm (x ‚à∑ xs) {ys} (here p)
    rewrite ++‚Åª‚àò++‚Å∫ ys {ys = x ‚à∑ xs} (inj‚ÇÇ (here p)) = refl
  ++-comm‚àò++-comm (x ‚à∑ xs)      (there p) with ++‚Åª xs p | ++-comm‚àò++-comm xs p
  ++-comm‚àò++-comm (x ‚à∑ xs) {ys} (there .([ ++‚Å∫ ≥ xs , ++‚Å∫À° ]‚Ä≤ (++‚Åª ys (++‚Å∫ ≥ ys p))))
    | inj‚ÇÅ p | refl
    rewrite ++‚Åª‚àò++‚Å∫ ys (inj‚ÇÇ                 p)
          | ++‚Åª‚àò++‚Å∫ ys (inj‚ÇÇ $ there {x = x} p) = refl
  ++-comm‚àò++-comm (x ‚à∑ xs) {ys} (there .([ ++‚Å∫ ≥ xs , ++‚Å∫À° ]‚Ä≤ (++‚Åª ys (++‚Å∫À° p))))
    | inj‚ÇÇ p | refl
    rewrite ++‚Åª‚àò++‚Å∫ ys {ys =     xs} (inj‚ÇÅ p)
          | ++‚Åª‚àò++‚Å∫ ys {ys = x ‚à∑ xs} (inj‚ÇÅ p) = refl
 
  ++‚Üî++ : ‚àÄ xs ys ‚Üí Any P (xs ++ ys) ‚Üî Any P (ys ++ xs)
  ++‚Üî++ xs ys = mk‚Üî‚Çõ‚Ä≤ (++-comm xs ys) (++-comm ys xs)
                        (++-comm‚àò++-comm ys) (++-comm‚àò++-comm xs)
 
  ++-insert : ‚àÄ xs {ys} ‚Üí P x ‚Üí Any P (xs ++ [ x ] ++ ys)
  ++-insert xs Px = ++‚Å∫ ≥ xs (++‚Å∫À° (singleton‚Å∫ Px))

-- concat
 
module _ {P : A ‚Üí Set p} where
 
  concat‚Å∫ : ‚àÄ {xss} ‚Üí Any (Any P) xss ‚Üí Any P (concat xss)
  concat‚Å∫ (here p)           = ++‚Å∫À° p
  concat‚Å∫ (there {x = xs} p) = ++‚Å∫ ≥ xs (concat‚Å∫ p)
 
  concat‚Åª : ‚àÄ xss ‚Üí Any P (concat xss) ‚Üí Any (Any P) xss
  concat‚Åª ([]       ‚à∑ xss) p         = there $ concat‚Åª xss p
  concat‚Åª ((x ‚à∑ xs) ‚à∑ xss) (here  p) = here (here p)
  concat‚Åª ((x ‚à∑ xs) ‚à∑ xss) (there p) with concat‚Åª (xs ‚à∑ xss) p
  ... | here  p‚Ä≤ = here (there p‚Ä≤)
  ... | there p‚Ä≤ = there p‚Ä≤
 
  concat‚Åª‚àò++‚Å∫À° : ‚àÄ {xs} xss (p : Any P xs) ‚Üí
                 concat‚Åª (xs ‚à∑ xss) (++‚Å∫À° p) ‚â° here p
  concat‚Åª‚àò++‚Å∫À° xss (here  p) = refl
  concat‚Åª‚àò++‚Å∫À° xss (there p) rewrite concat‚Åª‚àò++‚Å∫À° xss p = refl
 
  concat‚Åª‚àò++‚Å∫ ≥ : ‚àÄ xs xss (p : Any P (concat xss)) ‚Üí
                   concat‚Åª (xs ‚à∑ xss) (++‚Å∫ ≥ xs p) ‚â° there (concat‚Åª xss p)
  concat‚Åª‚àò++‚Å∫ ≥ []       xss p = refl
  concat‚Åª‚àò++‚Å∫ ≥ (x ‚à∑ xs) xss p rewrite concat‚Åª‚àò++‚Å∫ ≥ xs xss p = refl
 
  concat‚Å∫‚àòconcat‚Åª : ‚àÄ xss (p : Any P (concat xss)) ‚Üí
                      concat‚Å∫ (concat‚Åª xss p) ‚â° p
  concat‚Å∫‚àòconcat‚Åª ([]       ‚à∑ xss) p         = concat‚Å∫‚àòconcat‚Åª xss p
  concat‚Å∫‚àòconcat‚Åª ((x ‚à∑ xs) ‚à∑ xss) (here p)  = refl
  concat‚Å∫‚àòconcat‚Åª ((x ‚à∑ xs) ‚à∑ xss) (there p)
    with p | concat‚Åª (xs ‚à∑ xss) p | concat‚Å∫‚àòconcat‚Åª (xs ‚à∑ xss) p
  ... | .(++‚Å∫À° p‚Ä≤)              | here  p‚Ä≤ | refl = refl
  ... | .(++‚Å∫ ≥ xs (concat‚Å∫ p‚Ä≤)) | there p‚Ä≤ | refl = refl
 
  concat‚Åª‚àòconcat‚Å∫ : ‚àÄ {xss} (p : Any (Any P) xss) ‚Üí concat‚Åª xss (concat‚Å∫ p) ‚â° p
  concat‚Åª‚àòconcat‚Å∫ (here                      p) = concat‚Åª‚àò++‚Å∫À° _ p
  concat‚Åª‚àòconcat‚Å∫ (there {x = xs} {xs = xss} p)
    rewrite concat‚Åª‚àò++‚Å∫ ≥ xs xss (concat‚Å∫ p) =
      cong there $ concat‚Åª‚àòconcat‚Å∫ p
 
  concat‚Üî : ‚àÄ {xss} ‚Üí Any (Any P) xss ‚Üî Any P (concat xss)
  concat‚Üî {xss} = mk‚Üî‚Çõ‚Ä≤ concat‚Å∫ (concat‚Åª xss) (concat‚Å∫‚àòconcat‚Åª xss) concat‚Åª‚àòconcat‚Å∫

-- cartesianProductWith
 
module _ (f : A ‚Üí B ‚Üí C) where
 
  cartesianProductWith‚Å∫ : (‚àÄ {x y} ‚Üí P x ‚Üí Q y ‚Üí R (f x y)) ‚Üí
                          Any P xs ‚Üí Any Q ys ‚Üí
                          Any R (cartesianProductWith f xs ys)
  cartesianProductWith‚Å∫ pres (here  px)  qys = ++‚Å∫À° (map‚Å∫ (Any.map (pres px) qys))
  cartesianProductWith‚Å∫ pres (there qxs) qys = ++‚Å∫ ≥ _ (cartesianProductWith‚Å∫ pres qxs qys)
 
  cartesianProductWith‚Åª : (‚àÄ {x y} ‚Üí R (f x y) ‚Üí P x √ó Q y) ‚Üí ‚àÄ xs ys ‚Üí
                          Any R (cartesianProductWith f xs ys) ‚Üí
                          Any P xs √ó Any Q ys
  cartesianProductWith‚Åª resp (x ‚à∑ xs) ys Rxsys with ++‚Åª (map (f x) ys) Rxsys
  ... | inj‚ÇÅ Rfxys = let Rxys = map‚Åª Rfxys
    in here (proj‚ÇÅ (resp (proj‚ÇÇ (Any.satisfied Rxys)))) , Any.map (proj‚ÇÇ ‚àò resp) Rxys
  ... | inj‚ÇÇ Rc    = let pxs , qys = cartesianProductWith‚Åª resp xs ys Rc
    in there pxs , qys
 
------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- cartesianProduct
 
cartesianProduct‚Å∫ : Any P xs ‚Üí Any Q ys ‚Üí
                    Any (P ‚ü®√ó‚ü© Q) (cartesianProduct xs ys)
cartesianProduct‚Å∫ = cartesianProductWith‚Å∫ _,_ _,_
 
cartesianProduct‚Åª : ‚àÄ xs ys ‚Üí Any (P ‚ü®√ó‚ü© Q) (cartesianProduct xs ys) ‚Üí
                    Any P xs √ó Any Q ys
cartesianProduct‚Åª = cartesianProductWith‚Åª _,_ id
 
------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- applyUpTo
 
applyUpTo‚Å∫ : ‚àÄ f {i n} ‚Üí P (f i) ‚Üí i < n ‚Üí Any P (applyUpTo f n)
applyUpTo‚Å∫ _ p z<s       = here p
applyUpTo‚Å∫ f p (s<s i<n@(s‚â§s _)) =
  there (applyUpTo‚Å∫ (f ‚àò suc) p i<n)
 
applyUpTo‚Åª : ‚àÄ f {n} ‚Üí Any P (applyUpTo f n) ‚Üí
             ‚àÉ Œª i ‚Üí i < n √ó P (f i)
applyUpTo‚Åª f {suc n} (here p)  = zero , z<s , p
applyUpTo‚Åª f {suc n} (there p) =
  let i , i<n , q = applyUpTo‚Åª (f ‚àò suc) p in suc i , s<s i<n , q
 
------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- applyDownFrom
 
applyDownFrom‚Å∫ : ‚àÄ f {i n} ‚Üí P (f i) ‚Üí i < n ‚Üí Any P (applyDownFrom f n)
applyDownFrom‚Å∫ f {i} {suc n} p (s‚â§s i‚â§n) with i ‚âü n
... | yes refl = here p
... | no  i‚â¢n  = there (applyDownFrom‚Å∫ f p (‚â§‚àß‚â¢‚áí< i‚â§n i‚â¢n))
 
applyDownFrom‚Åª : ‚àÄ f {n} ‚Üí Any P (applyDownFrom f n) ‚Üí
                 ‚àÉ Œª i ‚Üí i < n √ó P (f i)
applyDownFrom‚Åª f {suc n} (here p)  = n , ‚â§-refl , p
applyDownFrom‚Åª f {suc n} (there p) =
  let i , i<n , q = applyDownFrom‚Åª f p in i , m<n‚áím<1+n i<n , q
 
------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- tabulate
 
tabulate‚Å∫ : ‚àÄ {n} {f : Fin n ‚Üí A} i ‚Üí P (f i) ‚Üí Any P (tabulate f)
tabulate‚Å∫ zero    p = here p
tabulate‚Å∫ (suc i) p = there (tabulate‚Å∫ i p)
 
tabulate‚Åª : ‚àÄ {n} {f : Fin n ‚Üí A} ‚Üí Any P (tabulate f) ‚Üí ‚àÉ Œª i ‚Üí P (f i)
tabulate‚Åª {n = suc _} (here p)  = zero , p
tabulate‚Åª {n = suc _} (there p) = Product.map suc id (tabulate‚Åª p)

-- filter
 
module _ (Q? : U.Decidable Q) where
 
  filter‚Å∫ : (p : Any P xs) ‚Üí Any P (filter Q? xs) ‚äé ¬¨ Q (Any.lookup p)
  filter‚Å∫ {xs = x ‚à∑ _} (here px) with Q? x
  ... | true  because _     = inj‚ÇÅ (here px)
  ... | false because [¬¨Qx] = inj‚ÇÇ (invert [¬¨Qx])
  filter‚Å∫ {xs = x ‚à∑ _} (there p) with does (Q? x)
  ... | true  = Sum.map‚ÇÅ there (filter‚Å∫ p)
  ... | false = filter‚Å∫ p
 
  filter‚Åª : Any P (filter Q? xs) ‚Üí Any P xs
  filter‚Åª {xs = x ‚à∑ xs} p with does (Q? x) | p
  ... | true  | here px   = here px
  ... | true  | there pxs = there (filter‚Åª pxs)
  ... | false | pxs       = there (filter‚Åª pxs)

-- derun and deduplicate
 
module _ {R : Rel A r} (R? : B.Decidable R) where
 
  private
    derun‚Å∫-aux : ‚àÄ x xs ‚Üí P Respects R ‚Üí P x ‚Üí Any P (derun R? (x ‚à∑ xs))
    derun‚Å∫-aux x [] resp Px = here Px
    derun‚Å∫-aux x (y ‚à∑ xs) resp Px with R? x y
    ... | true  because [Rxy] = derun‚Å∫-aux y xs resp (resp (invert [Rxy]) Px)
    ... | false because _     = here Px
 
  derun‚Å∫ : P Respects R ‚Üí Any P xs ‚Üí Any P (derun R? xs)
  derun‚Å∫ {xs = x ‚à∑ xs}     resp (here px)   = derun‚Å∫-aux x xs resp px
  derun‚Å∫ {xs = x ‚à∑ y ‚à∑ xs} resp (there pxs) with does (R? x y)
  ... | true  = derun‚Å∫ resp pxs
  ... | false = there (derun‚Å∫ resp pxs)
 
  deduplicate‚Å∫ : ‚àÄ {xs} ‚Üí P Respects (flip R) ‚Üí Any P xs ‚Üí Any P (deduplicate R? xs)
  deduplicate‚Å∫ {xs = x ‚à∑ xs} resp (here px)   = here px
  deduplicate‚Å∫ {xs = x ‚à∑ xs} resp (there pxs)
    with filter‚Å∫ (¬¨? ‚àò R? x) (deduplicate‚Å∫ resp pxs)
  ... | inj‚ÇÅ p   = there p
  ... | inj‚ÇÇ ¬¨¬¨q =
    let q = decidable-stable (R? x (Any.lookup (deduplicate‚Å∫ resp pxs))) ¬¨¬¨q
    in  here (resp q (lookup-result (deduplicate‚Å∫ resp pxs)))
 
  private
    derun‚Åª-aux : Any P (derun R? (x ‚à∑ xs)) ‚Üí Any P (x ‚à∑ xs)
    derun‚Åª-aux {x = x} {[]}    (here px) = here px
    derun‚Åª-aux {x = x} {y ‚à∑ _} p[x‚à∑y‚à∑xs] with does (R? x y) | p[x‚à∑y‚à∑xs]
    ... | true  | p[y‚à∑xs]        = there (derun‚Åª-aux p[y‚à∑xs])
    ... | false | here px        = here px
    ... | false | there p[y‚à∑xs]! = there (derun‚Åª-aux p[y‚à∑xs]!)
 
  derun‚Åª : Any P (derun R? xs) ‚Üí Any P xs
  derun‚Åª {xs = x ‚à∑ xs} p[x‚à∑xs]! = derun‚Åª-aux p[x‚à∑xs]!
 
  deduplicate‚Åª : Any P (deduplicate R? xs) ‚Üí Any P xs
  deduplicate‚Åª {xs = x ‚à∑ _} (here px)    = here px
  deduplicate‚Åª {xs = x ‚à∑ _} (there pxs!) = there (deduplicate‚Åª (filter‚Åª (¬¨? ‚àò R? x) pxs!))

-- mapWith‚àà.
 
module _ {P : B ‚Üí Set p} where
 
  mapWith‚àà‚Å∫ : ‚àÄ {xs : List A} (f : ‚àÄ {x} ‚Üí x ‚àà xs ‚Üí B) ‚Üí
                (‚àÉ‚ÇÇ Œª x (x‚ààxs : x ‚àà xs) ‚Üí P (f x‚ààxs)) ‚Üí
                Any P (mapWith‚àà xs f)
  mapWith‚àà‚Å∫ f (_ , here refl  , p) = here p
  mapWith‚àà‚Å∫ f (_ , there x‚ààxs , p) =
    there $ mapWith‚àà‚Å∫ (f ‚àò there) (_ , x‚ààxs , p)
 
  mapWith‚àà‚Åª : ‚àÄ (xs : List A) (f : ‚àÄ {x} ‚Üí x ‚àà xs ‚Üí B) ‚Üí
                Any P (mapWith‚àà xs f) ‚Üí
                ‚àÉ‚ÇÇ Œª x (x‚ààxs : x ‚àà xs) ‚Üí P (f x‚ààxs)
  mapWith‚àà‚Åª (y ‚à∑ xs) f (here  p) = (y , here refl , p)
  mapWith‚àà‚Åª (y ‚à∑ xs) f (there p) =
    Product.map‚ÇÇ (Product.map there id) $ mapWith‚àà‚Åª xs (f ‚àò there) p
 
  mapWith‚àà‚Üî : ‚àÄ {xs : List A} {f : ‚àÄ {x} ‚Üí x ‚àà xs ‚Üí B} ‚Üí
                (‚àÉ‚ÇÇ Œª x (x‚ààxs : x ‚àà xs) ‚Üí P (f x‚ààxs)) ‚Üî Any P (mapWith‚àà xs f)
  mapWith‚àà‚Üî = mk‚Üî‚Çõ‚Ä≤ (mapWith‚àà‚Å∫ _) (mapWith‚àà‚Åª _ _) (to‚àòfrom _ _) (from‚àòto _)
    where
    from‚àòto : ‚àÄ {xs : List A} (f : ‚àÄ {x} ‚Üí x ‚àà xs ‚Üí B)
              (p : ‚àÉ‚ÇÇ Œª x (x‚ààxs : x ‚àà xs) ‚Üí P (f x‚ààxs)) ‚Üí
              mapWith‚àà‚Åª xs f (mapWith‚àà‚Å∫ f p) ‚â° p
    from‚àòto f (_ , here refl  , p) = refl
    from‚àòto f (_ , there x‚ààxs , p)
      rewrite from‚àòto (f ‚àò there) (_ , x‚ààxs , p) = refl
 
    to‚àòfrom : ‚àÄ (xs : List A) (f : ‚àÄ {x} ‚Üí x ‚àà xs ‚Üí B)
              (p : Any P (mapWith‚àà xs f)) ‚Üí
              mapWith‚àà‚Å∫ f (mapWith‚àà‚Åª xs f p) ‚â° p
    to‚àòfrom (y ‚à∑ xs) f (here  p) = refl
    to‚àòfrom (y ‚à∑ xs) f (there p) =
      cong there $ to‚àòfrom xs (f ‚àò there) p
 
------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- reverse
 
reverseAcc‚Å∫ : ‚àÄ acc xs ‚Üí Any P acc ‚äé Any P xs ‚Üí Any P (reverseAcc acc xs)
reverseAcc‚Å∫ acc []       (inj‚ÇÅ ps)        = ps
reverseAcc‚Å∫ acc (x ‚à∑ xs) (inj‚ÇÅ ps)        = reverseAcc‚Å∫ (x ‚à∑ acc) xs (inj‚ÇÅ (there ps))
reverseAcc‚Å∫ acc (x ‚à∑ xs) (inj‚ÇÇ (here px)) = reverseAcc‚Å∫ (x ‚à∑ acc) xs (inj‚ÇÅ (here px))
reverseAcc‚Å∫ acc (x ‚à∑ xs) (inj‚ÇÇ (there y)) = reverseAcc‚Å∫ (x ‚à∑ acc) xs (inj‚ÇÇ y)
 
reverseAcc‚Åª : ‚àÄ acc xs ‚Üí Any P (reverseAcc acc xs) ‚Üí Any P acc ‚äé Any P xs
reverseAcc‚Åª acc []       ps = inj‚ÇÅ ps
reverseAcc‚Åª acc (x ‚à∑ xs) ps with reverseAcc‚Åª (x ‚à∑ acc) xs ps
... | inj‚ÇÅ (here px) = inj‚ÇÇ (here px)
... | inj‚ÇÅ (there pxs) = inj‚ÇÅ pxs
... | inj‚ÇÇ pxs = inj‚ÇÇ (there pxs)
 
reverse‚Å∫ : Any P xs ‚Üí Any P (reverse xs)
reverse‚Å∫ ps = reverseAcc‚Å∫ [] _ (inj‚ÇÇ ps)
 
reverse‚Åª : Any P (reverse xs) ‚Üí Any P xs
reverse‚Åª ps with inj‚ÇÇ pxs ‚Üê reverseAcc‚Åª [] _ ps = pxs
 
------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- pure
 
pure‚Å∫ : P x ‚Üí Any P (pure x)
pure‚Å∫ = here
 
pure‚Åª : Any P (pure x) ‚Üí P x
pure‚Åª (here p) = p
 
pure‚Å∫‚àòpure‚Åª : (p : Any P (pure x)) ‚Üí pure‚Å∫ (pure‚Åª p) ‚â° p
pure‚Å∫‚àòpure‚Åª (here p) = refl
 
pure‚Åª‚àòpure‚Å∫ : (p : P x) ‚Üí pure‚Åª {P = P} (pure‚Å∫ p) ‚â° p
pure‚Åª‚àòpure‚Å∫ p = refl
 
pure‚Üî : P x ‚Üî Any P (pure x)
pure‚Üî {P = P} = mk‚Üî‚Çõ‚Ä≤ pure‚Å∫ pure‚Åª pure‚Å∫‚àòpure‚Åª (pure‚Åª‚àòpure‚Å∫ {P = P})

-- _‚à∑_
 
‚à∑‚Üî : (P : Pred A p) ‚Üí (P x ‚äé Any P xs) ‚Üî Any P (x ‚à∑ xs)
‚à∑‚Üî {x = x} {xs} P =
  (P x         ‚äé Any P xs)  ‚Üî‚ü® pure‚Üî ‚äé-cong (Any P xs ‚àé) ‚ü©
  (Any P [ x ] ‚äé Any P xs)  ‚Üî‚ü® ++‚Üî ‚ü©
  Any P (x ‚à∑ xs)            ‚àé
  where open Related.EquationalReasoning

-- _>>=_
 
module _ {A B : Set ‚Ñì} {P : B ‚Üí Set p} {f : A ‚Üí List B} where
 
  >>=‚Üî : Any (Any P ‚àò f) xs ‚Üî Any P (xs >>= f)
